nodes.text: The commander of an Imperial Security Bureau black site at the Wretch of Tayron surrendered to the Rebel Alliance special forces team known as the Pathfinders during their raid on the base several weeks after the Battle of Endor. His surrender allowed the Rebels to gain access to critical intelligence needed in order to uncover and fight back against Operation: Cinder, an Imperial campaign to render countless worlds uninhabitable in the aftermath of the Emperor's demise.
